                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-04-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 30, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>British minister for foreign affairs asks me to inform him exact term President’s
                    instructions authorizing British officers to arrest the United States vessels
                    contravening act of Congress as proclaimed.</p>
            </div>
